      "span_text": "The objectives of this study were to adapt the ICQ, which was originally developed for adults with a chronic condition [CITATION_1] , for use in parents of an ill child (Illness Cognition Questionnaire-Parent version (ICQ-P)), to assess its psychometric properties, and to determine whether scores are associated with parental distress.",
